  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They wouldn't take you in the army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But-- but maybe you can do something for us, to take us in the Waffen-SS, whether we would agree to that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Well, obviously, we said we agreed to it very happily, would get us out of prison.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Probably not a wise choice had I known what these units were like, that they're just used to hunt up mines, clear minefields, with no-- no chance of survival.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So fortunately, it never materialized.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But somehow, this guy must have gotten the knack that he had these Jews in front of him with that phony offense, obviously, kids who just had been to high school, learned Latin and Greek, knew nothing about the world.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And-- and I think this must have to do with it, and, of course, also speaking fluent German and more than German because German, much more than an English, your class background reflects itself in the kind of language you speak.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So while these guys, of course, all spoke lower-class dialect, we spoke beautiful, high German.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I mean, that marked us instantly as being ruling class.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I think, putting all of these together, we spoke proper German, we-- we-- we knew how to stand at attention, we had very military manners, you know, we talked with a clipped accent, the way they liked it, we were never tortured as many people were on these occasions, I think just for the fun of the interrogating officers.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after we had signed this thing and they had kindly offered us the help in getting us into the Waffen-SS, we were sent home, put in a car, and sent back to the cell, never to be seen again.",
      "word_count": 40
    }
  ],
